text: Parks and Wildlife Commission of the Northern Territory is the Northern Territory Government agency which aim for tasks such as the establishment of "parks, reserves, sanctuaries and other land", the management of these and the "protection, conservation, sustainable use of wildlife etc.https://legislation.nt.gov.au/api/sitecore/Act/Word_History?id=16214 == References == Category:Northern Territory Category:Government agencies of Australia
